    proc resolve_target_link_dependencies from analyzer
    proc resolve_target_dependencies from analyzer
    proc resolve_variable_references from analyzer
    proc build_cmake_dependency_graph from analyzer
End Process

Process called "resolve_target_link_dependencies" takes analyzer as Integer:
    Note: Resolve target_link_libraries dependencies

    @Reasoning:
    Analyze target_link_libraries commands to build link dependency graph.
    Validate linked targets exist and are compatible with linking target
